            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Asset_62_707dff3c-16db-4ac6-8a97-9fa6e7b7af99.webp",
            "image_position": "center center",
            "heading": "> Muga Silk - Never seen in skincare before",
            "description": "<p>Introducing liquified Golden Muga Silk, a pioneering innovation in skincare. Celebrated for its strength, beauty, and lustrous appearance resembling spun gold, this silk brings unprecedented qualities to skincare. It has regenerative and healing properties so profound that it’s even used in surgical procedures.</p>",
            "button_label": "",
