            "button_size": "medium",
            "button_style_secondary": false
          }
        },
        "image_Yf3dni": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Asset_61_032dbb70-7130-4d26-8d05-d2f98d63853c.webp",
            "image_position": "center center",
            "heading": "> Origin of Golden Muga Silk",
            "description": "<p>Originating from Northeast India, particularly Assam, Golden Muga Silk is renowned for its exceptional durability and cultural significance in weaving silk sarees. The fabric is so robust and long-lasting that it is said to outlive its wearer.</p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_size": "medium",
            "button_style_secondary": false
          }
        },
        "image_rirt8c": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Asset_60_08030103-8f50-4230-87d8-ea905c166136.webp",
            "image_position": "center center",
            "heading": "> Protein Properties of Muga Silk",
            "description": "<p>Muga Silk's 97% protein polymer composition is revered for its regenerative and healing properties. It reduces water loss, strengthens skin resilience, and diminishes the appearance of wrinkles, offering profound benefits rooted in skin science.</p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_size": "medium",
            "button_style_secondary": false
          }
        },
        "image_jMpJqT": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Asset_59_a34fa013-4552-4787-94ee-9c10199084a6.webp",
            "image_position": "center center",
            "heading": "> Liquified Muga Silk in Amrutini®",
            "description": "<p>Leveraging proprietary techniques, Muga Silk has been liquefied & integrated into our Amrutini® line. Offering skin-strengthening benefits, this represents a breakthrough - that has never-before been seen in skincare.</p>",
