    "testimonials_cRyJkN": {
      "type": "testimonials",
      "blocks": {
        "testimonial_cnHPdC": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "5",
            "text": "<p>“I think I just found a magic eraser for my smile lines. I have been using the Freedom of Expression Line Limiter for a while now and I am genuinely surprised to see how much it has helped my smile lines. I seriously love this stuff.”</p>",
            "author": "Tiffany"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_D7eCcD": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "5",
            "text": "<p>“They are heaven! The Amrutini Luminosity Dewdrops make my nighttime skin routine feel like a pre-bed facial. The serum is nourishing but also light, so I wake up with refreshed skin without leaving an oil slick on my pillow. Also, the silk cocoons (used for gentle exfoliation) are the cherry on top of the cake. This routine is my five minutes of luxury that helps me unwind before bed.”</p>",
            "author": "Karen"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_DPdtBK": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "5",
            "text": "<p>“I am completely enamored with the Broadway Detox Mask. In a mere 10 minutes, this remarkable mask has performed a miraculous transformation on my skin, leaving it not only exceptionally radiant but also incredibly glowy. Its one the finest detox masks I've ever came across.”</p>",
            "author": "Natalia"
          }
        }
      },
